CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper January 26, 1946, pg. 4, reads: "Meet At Home - After traveling half way around the world, these servicemen met in Pittsburgh last week. Left to right: Johnny Wilson, Pvt. Leonard Martin, stationed at Tuskegee, Ala.; Sgt. Elwood N. Martin, just back from the South Pacific and Europe; T/4 Bryant E. Prentice, recently discharged after service in the Pacific area, and G. Prentice his brother. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Servicemen Johnny Wilson, Pvt. Leonard Martin, Sgt. Elwood N. Martin, T/4 Bryant E. Prentice, and G. Prentice posed in Harris Studio
